ure..charterers to allow vsl to drift offshore for safety reasons"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-02T17:05:05.213","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl was able to burn VLSFO with visc lower than 70 cst through the canal rather than needing to switch to LSMGO. Saved 65k in fuel"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-21T14:13:36.46","modifiedByFull":"Mohlin, Max","remark":"Arrival bunkers Panama Canal updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-15T14:29:39.997","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended time at Panama Canal. First 24 hours our account, following for charterers."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-13T16:39:11.06","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Panama Canal costs less than generated basis no prebooking."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-11T13:59:52.733","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Discharge port likely to be La Pampilla"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}